<L>__{exterior street full shot}
<A>__{as macreedy, after a moment's hesitation, starts down it. from the far end, at the telegraph agent's shack, a figure starts running toward macreedy. it is hastings. intercut : between the two men. hastings, in his concentration, doesn't see the stranger until he is almost upon him. he slows down, suddenly, awkwardly, to a self conscious walk. macreedy grins at him, passes on, shaking his head speculatively. hastings, with a parting glance, gallops up the hotel steps.}
